description:
Add Project README Documentation

Create a comprehensive README.md file that helps users understand, install, and use the project effectively.

Requirements:
- Add a clear project title and concise description of what it does
- Include installation/setup instructions with prerequisites
- Provide basic usage examples or quick-start guide
- Document any configuration options or environment variables
- List key dependencies and system requirements
- Add license information if applicable

Considerations:
- Review existing code to accurately describe project functionality
- Match the tone and detail level to the project's complexity
- Include any build/run commands specific to the project
- Add badges for build status, version, or coverage if CI is configured
